<item>
            <title>[LU-13209] SUSE 15 SP2 client build fix</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13209</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;SUSE 15 SP2 kernel is based on 5.3.18&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This linux kernel change&#160;v5.2-rc4-45-g051f278e9d81&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;KBUILD_SRC := $(abs_srctree)&lt;br/&gt;
&#160; &#160;to&lt;br/&gt;
building_out_of_srctree := 1&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;breaks module building post configuration.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;While embedded in autoMakefile.am is:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;.... $(if&#160;&lt;em&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#FF0000&quot;&gt;$$(KBUILD_SRC)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/em&gt;,-Iinclude2 -I$$(srctree)/include) ...&lt;br/&gt;
This should now be&lt;br/&gt;
&#160;.... $(if &lt;em&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#FF0000&quot;&gt;$$(KBUILDSRC)$$(building_out_of_srctree)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/em&gt;,-Iinclude2 -I$$(srctree)/include) ...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To cover both pre and post 5.3 kernels.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
